snippet.title: System Invaders - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience waves upon waves of viruses that have infected your computer. 5 Chapters with over 125 Waves of enemies! Play with your friends in local or online co-op! Can you destroy all the viruses?

Check out System Invaders on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1253110

Join the official Prisma Games server on Discord:
https://discord.gg/prismagames
